org.joone.net
Class NetCheck

java.lang.Object
  org.joone.net.NetCheck
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class NetCheck
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable

Class to represent a network validation check error. NetChecks of ERROR severity prevent the network from running, NetChecks of WARNING severity do not.
